"854","SIGNATURE   HARRIS COHEN"
"855","TITLE       MGR ADMINISTRATION"
"856","</TEXT>"
"857","</DOCUMENT>"
"858","<DOCUMENT>"
"859","<TYPE>EX-99.77B ACCT LTTR"
"860","<SEQUENCE>2"
"861","<FILENAME>icletter.txt"
"862","<DESCRIPTION>INTERNAL CONTROL LETTER"
"863","<TEXT>"
"864","REPORT OF INDEPENDENT"
"865","REGISTERED PUBLIC ACCOUNTING"
"866","FIRM"
"867","To the Shareholders of SCA Absolute"
"868","Return Fund and SCA Directional"
"869","Fund and"
"870","Board of Trustees of Northern Lights"
"871","Fund Trust"
"872","In planning and performing our audits of"
"873","the financial statements of SCA"
"874","Absolute Return Fund and SCA"
"875","Directional Fund, each a series of"
"876","shares of beneficial interest of Northern"
"877","Lights Fund Trust (the Funds), as of"
"878","and for the year ended June 30, 2013,"
"879","in accordance with the standards of the"
"880","Public Company Accounting Oversight"
"881","Board (United States) (PCAOB), we"
"882","considered their internal control over"
"883","financial reporting, including control"
"884","activities for safeguarding securities, as"
"885","a basis for designing our auditing"
"886","procedures for the purpose of"
"887","expressing our opinion on the financial"
"888","statements and to comply with the"
"889","requirements of Form N-SAR, but not"
"890","for the purpose of expressing an opinion"
"891","on the effectiveness of the Funds'"
"892","internal control over financial reporting."
"893","Accordingly, we express no such"
"894","opinion."
"895","The management of Northern Lights"
"896","Fund Trust is responsible for"
"897","establishing and maintaining effective"
"898","internal control over financial reporting."
"899","In fulfilling this responsibility, estimates"
"900","and judgments by management are"
"901","required to assess the expected benefits"
"902","and related costs of controls.  A"
"903","company's internal control over financial"
"904","reporting is a process designed to"
"905","provide reasonable assurance regarding"
"906","the reliability of financial reporting and"
"907","the preparation of financial statements"
"908","for external purposes in accordance with"
"909","accounting principles generally"
"910","accepted in the United States of"
"911","America (GAAP).  A company's"
"912","internal control over financial reporting"
"913","includes those policies and procedures"
"914","that (1) pertain to the maintenance of"
"915","records that, in reasonable detail,"
"916","accurately and fairly reflect the"
"917","transactions and dispositions of the"
"918","assets of the company; (2) provide"
"919","reasonable assurance that transactions"
"920","are recorded as necessary to permit"
"921","preparation of the financial statements"
"922","in accordance with GAAP, and that"
"923","receipts and expenditures of the"
"924","company are being made only in"
"925","accordance with authorizations of"
"926","management and trustees of the"
"927","company; and (3) provide reasonable"
"928","assurance regarding prevention or"
"929","timely detection of unauthorized"
"930","acquisition, use or disposition of a"
"931","company's assets that could have a"
"932","material effect on the financial"
"933","statements."
"934","Because of inherent limitations, internal"
"935","control over financial reporting may not"
"936","prevent or detect misstatements.  Also,"
"937","projections of any evaluation of"
"938","effectiveness to future periods are"
"939","subject to the risk that controls may"
"940","become inadequate because of"
"941","changes in conditions or that the degree"
"942","of compliance with the policies or"
"943","procedures may deteriorate."
"944","A deficiency in internal control over"
"945","financial reporting exists when the"
"946","design or operation of a control does not"
"947","allow management or employees, in the"
"948","normal course of performing their"
"949","assigned functions, to prevent or detect"
"950","misstatements on a timely basis. A"
"951","material weakness is a deficiency, or"
"952","combination of deficiencies, in internal"
"953","control over financial reporting, such"
"954","that there is a reasonable possibility that"
"955","a material misstatement of the Funds'"
"956","annual or interim financial statements"
"957","will not be prevented or detected on a"
"958","timely basis."
"959","Our consideration of the Funds' internal"
"960","control over financial reporting was for"
"961","the limited purpose described in the first"
"962","paragraph and would not necessarily"
"963","disclose all deficiencies in internal"
"964","control that might be material"
"965","weaknesses under standards"
"966","established by the PCAOB.  However,"
"967","we noted no deficiencies in the internal"
"968","control over financial reporting and its"
"969","operations, including controls for"
"970","safeguarding securities that we consider"
"971","to be material weaknesses, as defined"
"972","above, as of June 30, 2013."
"973","This report is intended solely for the"
"974","information and use of management, the"
"975","shareholders of SCA Absolute Return"
"976","Fund and SCA Directional Fund, the"
"977","Board of Trustees of Northern Lights"
"978","Fund Trust and the Securities and"
"979","Exchange Commission and is not"
"980","intended to be and should not be used"
"981","by anyone other than these specified"
"982","parties."
"983","		BBD, LLP"
"984","Philadelphia, Pennsylvania"
"985","August 28, 2013"
